                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The United Nations Special Committee on the Balkans adopted its second interim
                    report on January 10, 1948; for text, see United Nations document A/522, dated
                    January 19, 1948. Excerpts from the report were included in Department of State,
                        <hi rend="italic">Documents &amp; State Papers</hi>, September 1948, page
                    375.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
